// IDX_conversation_participants_userId
// IDX_conversation_participants_conversationId
// IDX_conversation_participants_userId_conversationId (unique)

// message
// IDX_message_conversationId
// IDX_message_senderId
// IDX_message_created_at
// IDX_message_conversationId_created_at (critical for chat loading)

// conversation
// IDX_conversation_lastActivityAt (sort chat list)